episodes.title: Truth 2x2 Cult Kids - Welcome
episodes.description: Welcome to the Truth 2x2 Cult Kids Podcast, by your host Laura McConnell Conti This is a short intro to the podcast, what you can expect and some background on your host. The next eposide will be focused on the background of the Truth 2x2 Cult. Show Notes: Links to my work: Substack: https://substack.com/@fierceladyfeminist Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@fierceladyfeminist Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lauramc.au/ Website: https://www.lauramcconnell.com.au/ Links to Support: LBH good trauma informed, cult sensitive therapists and support are hard to find. Please persist and try to find one that works for you. If you’re in a tough spot right now, please know you’re not alone. Here are some links to AU NZ supports and therapists which might be useful. https://www.thereligioustraumacollective.com/ As an Australian CSA survivor, the best support I’ve accessed at my lowest points, has been through Survivor Hub - https://www.thesurvivorhub.org.au/ Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
